Character-specific relics (Sage only)
DONE:	Byrd carpet
		Boss relic: 
		Replaces Flying carpet. Start each combat with 3 Flight. If you have 1 or 2 Flight at the start of your turn, set it to 3 again.
DONE:	Cooking Book
		Common relic: 
		Start each combat with 1 Brewing.
	Ancient Magnet
		Uncommon relic: 
		Enemies have 1 less Strength per Artifact on them. You may use Artifact potions on enemies.

Other relics (for all characters)
	Red Beast Statue
		Uncommon relic:
		Potion rewards are ?% more likely to be uncommon or rare potions.
